property of DNA do you think is most essential

00:01:54.380 --> 00:01:57.270
to make an RNA copy? Do you think it's,

00:01:57.270 --> 00:02:01.200
that DNA is able to associate with histones? That

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:03.950
it can have a helical structure, the fact that

00:02:03.950 --> 00:02:07.900
it base pairs, or the fact that it's inherited from

